#

Cabbage and Beetroot Borscht

75 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A vibrant and hearty soup packed with earthy flavors and a touch of sweetness from beets, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beetroot: 3 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 1 small head, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • potato: 2 medium, diced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • vinegar: 1 tablespoon
